      "rationale": "Eleven non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw constructs were assembled from three production lots and distributed across two laboratories (n=6 Lab A, n=5 Lab B). Pre-test CMM confirmed all specimens within dimensional specification. Inter-laboratory coefficient of variation for stiffness was 4.7%. Gradation 3 achieved."
