      "rationale": "Each of the 11 FEA model instances was parameterized using specimen-specific CMM geometry and lot-specific material coupon data. Boundary conditions replicate the ASTM F1717 fixture geometry as measured. Input equivalency is fully documented; Gradation 3 achieved."
