      "rationale": "E/uval computed as 0.87, 1.12, and 1.31 for stiffness, yield force, and force at 40 mm displacement respectively. Percent differences are 3.2%, 6.8%, and 7.1%. All three QoIs pass both acceptance criteria across all specimens and both laboratories. Gradation 3 achieved."
