    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/nagaraja-credibility-assessment-team",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed their required gradation levels. The single shortfall (Test conditions, achieved Gradation 2 vs. required Gradation 3) is accepted on the basis that ASTM F1717 specifies a single quasi-static loading rate, Ti-6Al-4V ELI exhibits negligible strain-rate sensitivity in the relevant range, and the intended use does not involve dynamic loading. Overall model credibility is sufficient to support the regulatory submission decision. Note: this package conforms to ProfileMinimal; the signature workflow is pending and has not been applied. Structural integrity should be independently verified prior to regulatory reliance.",
